OL,4,G1440FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GThe competition takes place in
OL,6,     GLeeds, where Alice sows her
OL,7,     Gdinner party seeds. Can she win
OL,8,     Gher guests over with a ginormous
OL,9,     Gpavlova, and get the big score
OL,10,     Gshe needs? _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1515FCome Dine with Me
OL,12,     GNight two in Leeds and Andy's up
OL,13,     Gnext; will his posh nosh leave
OL,14,     Ghis guests perplexed? Fancy food,
OL,15,     Ga Ferrari and cocktail making;
OL,16,     Gwill he get good scores or a rude
OL,17,     Gawakening? _WorldPoetryDay
