OL,4,G1550FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GThird host in Leeds is student
OL,6,     GDanielle; will her guests be in
OL,7,     Gfood heaven or hell? After
OL,8,     Gserving dessert in her wedding
OL,9,     Gdress, one guest's proposal turns
OL,10,     Ginto a right mess. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1620FCome Dine with Me
OL,12,     GThe fourth host in Leeds is Matt,
OL,13,     Gwho seems to impress off the bat.
OL,14,     GBut not everyone's happy, for
OL,15,     Gsome it's quite crappy, and
OL,16,     Gdessert ends up going splat!
OL,17,     G_WorldPoetryDay
