OL,4,G1650FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GLast host in Leeds is jeweller
OL,6,     GLynne, who hopes her night
OL,7,     Gsparkles, but can she win? With
OL,8,     Gdinner done, it's karaoke galore;
OL,9,     Gonly one can triumph, who has the
OL,10,     Gtop score? _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1725FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe guests see what's hiding
OL,13,     Gwithin, Nyoami and Joe's The Trap
OL,14,     GInn. Will they like the decor?
OL,15,     GCould breakfast bring more? And
OL,16,     Gwill anyone spot a puffin?
OL,17,     G_WorldPoetryDay
