OL,4,G1755FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GDamian and also his husband
OL,6,     GNigel, welcome their guests to
OL,7,     Gthe Newholme Hotel. But what do
OL,8,     Gthey think of a surprise in the
OL,9,     Gloo? And a slimy breakfast causes
OL,10,     Gconcern too. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1825FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GTo Portsonachan Hotel & Lodges
OL,13,     Gthe B&Bers go, with a keen eye
OL,14,     Gfor detail and dust in tow. They
OL,15,     Gvisit Inveraray Castle on a
OL,16,     Gspooky trail, but will breakfast
OL,17,     Gbe an epic fail? _WorldPoetryDay
