OL,12,G2305F999: On the Front Line
OL,13,     GHurt head and breathless, and not
OL,14,     Gfeeling pain always, the
OL,15,     Gambulance comes. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,16,G0010F999: On the Front Line
OL,17,     GParamedics treat a man having an
OL,18,     Ganaphylactic reaction, a patient
OL,19,     Gwho's having a heart attack and a
OL,20,     Gman receiving chemotherapy who
OL,21,     Gmay have developed sepsis.
